en-US.title: Whatcom Family Medicine - Family Care Network
en-US.description: Whatcom Family Medicine, part of Family Care Network, is a locally owned and operated clinic committed to providing quality health care. The clinic strives to build strong relationships with patients, creating a rewarding and positive healthcare experience. The team of board-certified physicians is approachable and sincerely care about their patients. Conveniently located in Bellingham, the clinic offers a wide range of services, ensuring that the needs of the transgender community will be met with compassion and understanding.
